column5: Went to Canal Lake with my friend. The weather man was calling for afternoon rain so we've decided to start early.  6:00 am view    We've caught some bass, crappie, few "Canal Lake" size pikes ( 20-25") . Two pikes and crappie were invited for fish fry contest  This chunky fellow make my day ( 32" / 6 lb 8 oz ), my PB
Nice Pike! Congrats on your PB!!
Congrats on the PB. Thanks for sharing.
